{"tid":2415492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔為睇波，由荃灣步行往小西灣運動場","createTime":"2021-02-20T09:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T10:21:34.000Z","uid":36494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"70e7483da1b65a128a2624d98063cde99cc2b365","tid":2415492,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"復賽首仗被安排在較偏遠的小西灣運動場上演，開閘初期球迷人數不多，但網上討論區卻早已鬧得熱烘烘。<span class=\"red\">事緣「連登」討論區一名名為「鍾偉強」的會員早上發帖，指自己會由荃灣出發行路往小西灣入場。帖文短短時間已獲不少人「正評」支持，</span>更惹來愉園公關在Facebook專頁出文表示會贈送球賽門票。最終「鍾偉強」花了約6小時、於下午2時前抵達球場。他接受訪問時指，有此想法緣於想引起外界對復賽的關注：「昨晚突然有這個念頭，加上本身自己也喜歡行路，想趁復賽第一日引起大家注意。每場比賽我都很期待及會入場，但未必再行路了。」他笑言因已習慣行路，即使行了約23公里仍不太疲累，又謂入場安排尚算順暢，僅是檢查電子申報表時需時較久。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/321921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F321921&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=14970904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/321921</a>"},{"pid":"d1788e3eb0d99827bbd9aa56452959ddc388d18c","tid":2415492,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897e9d1589e10455d7db3dce7d31ddc13c0ff2b8","tid":2415492,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"[行路撚] 荃灣行去小西灣睇波！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2414976\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2414976</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n原post"},{"pid":"2aa06f8cd8e553c4bd65af0fb302d4b457ec40b5","tid":2415492,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3317f9cb5b2c2223418c362c5c1464402ea21d0","tid":2415492,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}